query:
/*+ NoHashJoin(a1 acc q1 s t1 tq1 u1 b) */ select acc.location,
count(*)
from question AS q1
inner join tag_question AS tq1
on q1.id = tq1.question_id AND q1.score >= 0 AND q1.score <= 0
inner join site AS s
on s.site_id = q1.site_id AND s.site_id = tq1.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('drupal',
'physics',
'pt')
inner join so_user AS u1
on s.site_id = u1.site_id AND u1.reputation >= 0 AND u1.reputation <= 10
inner join tag AS t1
on s.site_id = t1.site_id AND t1.id = tq1.tag_id AND t1.name IN ('6',
'blocks',
'c',
'classical-mechanics',
'commerce',
'electrostatics',
'fluid-dynamics',
'general-relativity',
'hooks',
'html5',
'laravel',
'waves')
inner join answer AS a1
on s.site_id = a1.site_id AND a1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND q1.id = a1.question_id
inner join account AS acc
on acc.id = u1.account_id
inner join badge AS b
on s.site_id = b.site_id AND b.user_id = u1.id AND b.name IN ('Autobiographer',
'Scholar',
'Student') group by acc.location order by count(*) desc LIMIT 100;
